  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>“When you look into A Bit of Tales, A Bit of Tales also looks into you.”</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Elyssa, Goddess of Dimension (She doesn't exist in your world.)</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3568300/extras/0ac5f923082bfe7bcc74103d255c8580.poster.avif?t=1767262653\" width=800 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3568300/extras/0ac5f923082bfe7bcc74103d255c8580.webm?t=1767262653\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3568300/extras/0ac5f923082bfe7bcc74103d255c8580.mp4?t=1767262653\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>In a Bit of Tales</strong> is a one-of-a-kind horror anthology game featuring 7 spine-chilling stories, delivered in an omakase-style experience. Explore haunting dreams, mysterious cults, ghostly schools, and more. Each tale is thoughtfully crafted to give a distinct and memorable horror experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3568300/extras/2b7df35a0bbd613ee5de411d9c174358.poster.avif?t=1767262653\" width=800 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3568300/extras/2b7df35a0bbd613ee5de411d9c174358.webm?t=1767262653\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3568300/extras/2b7df35a0bbd613ee5de411d9c174358.mp4?t=1767262653\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover 7 unique and chilling horror tales.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as the \"Protagonist\" and shape the outcome of each story.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience varied presentations, graphics, and gameplay styles for every story.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The average length of each \"Bit\" is 5-30 minutes.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3568300/extras/7266a81ad70d842585b18cef46d2f9e8.poster.avif?t=1767262653\" width=800 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3568300/extras/7266a81ad70d842585b18cef46d2f9e8.webm?t=1767262653\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3568300/extras/7266a81ad70d842585b18cef46d2f9e8.mp4?t=1767262653\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Explore \"Bits\"</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Maria: </strong>Face your nightmare—chaotic and unpredictable.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Metamorphosis: </strong>Do you remember what happened in the laboratory?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Slime Swamp: </strong>Humanity’s desires are endless… and she wishes to become a Slime Girl!?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Is It Truly Satan?: </strong>You are a devoted follower of The Satan, Cre’ne.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Shut Your Eyes:</strong> If you see it, it sees you. The restless spirits of this school are watching.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Butterfly's Lament: </strong>Take on the role of a loving boyfriend waiting for his beloved girlfriend.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Old Photograph:  </strong>A photograph that brings back memories of a tragic event…?</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3568300/extras/827a98f86a7203925af2fec2aec2ddf9.poster.avif?t=1767262653\" width=800 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3568300/extras/827a98f86a7203925af2fec2aec2ddf9.webm?t=1767262653\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3568300/extras/827a98f86a7203925af2fec2aec2ddf9.mp4?t=1767262653\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3568300/extras/a40cf73769527115ca8cddb054dddf49.poster.avif?t=1767262653\" width=800 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3568300/extras/a40cf73769527115ca8cddb054dddf49.webm?t=1767262653\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3568300/extras/a40cf73769527115ca8cddb054dddf49.mp4?t=1767262653\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>\"These tales were waiting for you. Once seen, they never let go.\"</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Daybloom Project</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3568300/extras/b68fc061d0ac82515f1db418d08b78f9.poster.avif?t=1767262653\" width=800 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3568300/extras/b68fc061d0ac82515f1db418d08b78f9.webm?t=1767262653\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3568300/extras/b68fc061d0ac82515f1db418d08b78f9.mp4?t=1767262653\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3568300/extras/fd23103affc4d562b4712f4cf48e8f2e.poster.avif?t=1767262653\" width=800 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3568300/extras/fd23103affc4d562b4712f4cf48e8f2e.webm?t=1767262653\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3568300/extras/fd23103affc4d562b4712f4cf48e8f2e.mp4?t=1767262653\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
